<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>클라이언트-서버 인터랙션 데모</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>클라이언트-서버 요청 실습</h1>

  <h2>1. GET 요청 (검색)</h2>
<form action="/search" method="get">
  값 1: <input type="text" name="value1" placeholder="사과">
  <br>
  값 2: <input type="text" name="value2" placeholder="바나나">
  <br>
  <button type="submit">검색</button>
</form>

  <h2>2. POST 요청 (댓글 작성)</h2>
